invariants:
  - Read this file at the start of every coding turn.
  - Preserve the exact root ranking kernel and stable debug hooks.
  - Do not reintroduce whole-document MutationObservers automatic reloads or click hijacking.
  - Every visible custom product control must come from the action contract.
  - Workspace writes resolve only after IndexedDB transaction completion.
  - Cancelled destructive actions must never be recorded as success.
  - Magic bytes and content outrank absent or contradictory MIME metadata.
  - Unknown binary must never be decoded into feed text.
  - Every local record may be deleted; shared assets may not be removed while referenced.
  - Stored blobs with empty type must be rendered using canonical record or asset MIME.
  - Flow Stage and Grid may change layout physics but never ranking records or action semantics.
  - Offscreen video may pause but must not mutate playback records or ranking state.
  - Titlebar owns product identity profile and status; commandbar owns commands and navigation.
  - Exactly one New action and one navigation container may exist.
  - No explanatory feed prose rounded SaaS cards or fake retro decoration.
  - Geolocation remains explicit and user initiated.
  - Never use or persist credentials pasted into chat.

